{"tid":2492722,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"希澈坦白學生時期最後悔抽菸「支氣管都壞了」！意外成高中教材","createTime":"2021-04-17T10:38:19.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-17T12:21:19.000Z","uid":16659,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"fedf52d7096595f17f766b3d26539d930872bfad","tid":2492722,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:38:19.000Z","msg":"南韓偶像男團Super Junior的希澈日前在節目上被問到學生時期最後悔的事情，他自己坦白，「學生時代最後悔的就是抽菸」，還表示因為抽菸關係，現在支氣管都損傷了，不過也意外成為了高中生的反面示範教材。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5571/d5571899.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5571%2Fd5571899.jpg&h=a7691023&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲希澈聊到徐太志與孩子們的夯曲。（圖／翻攝自KBS）<br />\n<br />\n希澈與女主持人金玟我在16日播出的綜藝節目《20世紀夯歌》，回顧了90年代的嘻哈夯曲，不得不提當年叱吒樂壇的「徐太志與孩子們」。<br />\n<br />\n而徐太志與孩子們瘋迷樂壇的招牌歌曲《Come Back Home》，便是出自徐太志的個人經驗，希澈向觀眾分享，「這是他以自身問題少年經驗所創作的歌曲，他當時還自己退學了，當年這種舉動是相當不可思議的。」也表示徐太志曾說成為問題少年讓他相當後悔。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5571/d5571897.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5571%2Fd5571897.jpg&h=b2e30211&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲希澈坦白學生時期最後悔抽菸「支氣管都壞了」。（圖／翻攝自KBS）<br />\n<br />\n女主持人便問希澈的學生生活過得如何？他回答，「覺得最後悔的事情之一就是在學生時代的時候抽菸，（因為吸菸）支氣管都造成了損傷。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/5571/d5571898.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F5571%2Fd5571898.jpg&h=6bc310bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲希澈後悔抽菸竟意外變成高中生教室裡反面教材。（圖／翻攝自KBS）<br />\n<br />\n不過讓希澈意外的是，「其實2011年我在《黃金漁場 Radio Star》主持就說過，（在學生時期）抽菸真的是讓我非常後悔，那時候我有個親戚弟弟是高中生，看到我在節目上說後悔在學生時代抽菸的話，就把他截圖貼在教室裡，他同學都說，『這不是你親戚哥哥嗎？』讓我到現在都記得。」女主持人笑說希澈意外成為了示範教材。"},{"pid":"3310f9062e148bab1a10b026cbb89a28834ef53a","tid":2492722,"uid":139173,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:40:18.000Z","msg":"「學生時代最後悔的就是抽菸，<span class=\"red\"><strong>應該早在哺乳時期就要抽</strong></span>」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4edf1925a4984efa2494378fe3534abae1dfd5e","tid":2492722,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:41:03.000Z","msg":"點解食佢唔死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f608d30ae2812824598acf967cab67f091adff3f","tid":2492722,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3310f9062e148bab1a10b026cbb89a28834ef53a","tid":2492722,"uid":139173,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:40:18.000Z","msg":"「學生時代最後悔的就是抽菸，<span class=\"red\"><strong>應該早在哺乳時期就要抽</strong></span>」<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:41:29.000Z","msg":"Momo對奶好敏感<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7a89f59ff86de11b0f680379c52874c179d6d4f","tid":2492722,"uid":93096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:44:50.000Z","msg":"希切老師....<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ae2d0b44f0ec71c7d525fd471b0067f85c8b2d0","tid":2492722,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"b4edf1925a4984efa2494378fe3534abae1dfd5e","tid":2492722,"uid":339805,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:41:03.000Z","msg":"點解食佢唔死<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-17T10:49:48.000Z","msg":"生肺癌啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3c95fc712f82d5f9b4213277ca0a5fddf14f6532","tid":2492722,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b7a